title: 213: 10 Takeaways from Week 4
itunes:title: 213: 10 Takeaways from Week 4
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks have you covered following all of the Week 4 action. Are the Seahawks back on track (2:13)? Is Larry Fitzgerald still the most clutch wide out in the NFL (6:23)? Does Denver have the best defense in the league (26:39)? All that and much more on this jam packed episode of Move the Stick presented by the Ford F-Series.
